TITLE: Disney tells employees it will provide ‘comprehensive access’ for reproductive care
SUMMARY: Disney told employees it will help pay for pregnancy-related care if they have to travel to a different state after the Supreme Court's Roe v. Wade decision.

TITLE: United Airlines pilots to get raises of more than 14%, 8 weeks of maternity leave in new contract
SUMMARY: United is the first of the major U.S. airlines to reach a contract agreement with a pilots labor union.

SUMMARY: Polestar's SPAC deal has closed, and it now plans an aggressive global expansion.

SUMMARY: Abortion no longer is a federal right with Roe v. Wade overturned. Supreme Court Justice Thomas now is eyeing cases related to gay rights and birth control.

SUMMARY: These are the stocks posting the largest moves before the bell.
